Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.21,0:00:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know about personality rehabilitation?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.13,0:00:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a secret I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.46,0:00:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Beware of this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.71,0:00:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They want you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.58,0:00:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What was the secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.21,0:00:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,My father knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.83,0:00:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,My brother too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.88,0:00:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to know the answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.42,0:00:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,This incident is a declaration of war\Nby Seiran
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.04,0:00:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,to the New Himuka Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.42,0:00:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why they retreated?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.04,0:00:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,So the assassination of Chairman Sumeragi...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.83,0:00:45.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it was orchestrated by\NKaren and the Seiran Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.42,0:00:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,From what I heard, half of our members\Nhave defected to Seiran.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.71,0:00:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.79,0:00:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We will restructure the remaining forces of OSF.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.50,0:00:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, you will carry out\Nyour mission as Platoon 01.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.79,0:01:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito will be your captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.92,0:01:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You want me as their captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.25,0:01:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,As I mentioned earlier, I need you to be a hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.96,0:01:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Become the hero who defends this country.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.13,0:01:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,SCARLET NEXUS
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.17,0:01:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,♫A crime in reality♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.50,0:01:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,♫For Heaven's sake♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.75,0:01:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Accepts any fake♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.71,0:01:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,♫And disappears piling the eternity in fantasy♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.25,0:01:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Won't take it at all, I get sick♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.63,0:01:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,♫A girl looking back♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.67,0:01:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Casts the miracle into the instant world♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.00,0:01:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Did you lie♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.96,0:01:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Did you lie♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.83,0:01:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Spit the venom♫
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.96,0:02:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I know why♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.67,0:02:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I've found a game of ecstasy♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.33,0:02:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Red Criminal gets life♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.83,0:02:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I've never been in love♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.38,0:02:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Don’t know when I started\Ngetting sick of this world♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.17,0:02:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♫We will fly♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.83,0:02:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Someday I won't be crying♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.46,0:02:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I've been sacrificing myself\Nnot to hurt anybody♫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.46,0:02:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.75,0:02:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? You just stopped moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.58,0:02:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"PURSUING NAGI"\NYuito.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.88,0:02:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,"PURSUING NAGI"\NI thought we were at the headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.83,0:03:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.13,0:03:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for the long wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.67,0:03:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I rejected all requests for an interview
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.21,0:03:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,to keep Crows away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.46,0:03:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Colonel Luka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.88,0:03:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You may address me as Luka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.79,0:03:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, you are the captain now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.13,0:03:21.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, why am I the captain?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.96,0:03:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.83,0:03:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.08,0:03:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito is weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.29,0:03:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wataru, is there any anomaly\Nwith Yuito's brain activities?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.67,0:03:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No, everything is normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.83,0:03:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been reassigned as Platoon 01 of OSF.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.21,0:03:39.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You are our new captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.79,0:03:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We are on patrol at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.00,0:03:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember now. We were meeting my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.67,0:03:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't remember what happened next.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.79,0:03:56.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I ask him about the country's secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.67,0:03:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really not remember anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.67,0:04:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a bad feeling about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.50,0:04:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We should send him to the OSF hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.46,0:04:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're not feeling well, I can inform\Nthe superior for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.38,0:04:14.88,Default,,0,0,0,,My uncle is the hospital's Chief Director.\NI'll contact him for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.88,0:04:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,If I message him,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.83,0:04:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,he can have you checked in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.08,0:04:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,We will stay to carry out the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.79,0:04:27.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, you're the captain.\NWe can ask you to risk your health.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.92,0:04:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's best to have a doctor look at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.71,0:04:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Yuito?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Now,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I will announce the result of\NSeiran OSF structure.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.88,0:04:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Platoon 01.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.58,0:04:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Kyoka Eden.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.29,0:04:49.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Arashi Spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.13,0:04:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagero Donne.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.75,0:04:52.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiden Ritter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.63,0:04:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Haruka Frazer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.58,0:04:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Kasane Randall.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.25,0:05:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,New Himuka wasn't satisfied\Nwith social management,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.17,0:05:08.00,Default,,0,0,0,,so they started the forbidden experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.00,0:05:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Experiments to turn humans into Others.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.08,0:05:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They were researching a way\Nto create outstanding power users.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.21,0:05:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,During the process,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.58,0:05:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,they developed the experiment\Nto turn creatures into Others.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.08,0:05:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to overthrow the New Himuka government\Nthat conducted those horrible experiments.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You should come to Seiran.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.38,0:05:31.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it New Himuka that turn\NNaomi into a monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.42,0:05:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.75,0:05:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Naomi is in Seiran.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.13,0:05:37.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you save her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.25,0:05:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I will do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.38,0:05:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:44.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall go to Seiran as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.29,0:05:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't expect to see all of you in Seiran.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.38,0:05:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Seiran was my hometown anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.50,0:06:01.00,Default,,0,0,0,,And I despise New Himuka's conduct.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.00,0:06:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just killing time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.42,0:06:06.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Lady Kyoka is here too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.25,0:06:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a fan of Karen's?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.08,0:06:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it so surprising that I'm his fan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.42,0:06:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.17,0:06:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.08,0:06:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,As a commander,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.63,0:06:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm against the government's\Nsuspicious actions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.71,0:06:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to mention they conducted\Nexperiments to turn humans into Others.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.88,0:06:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's unforgivable.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.75,0:06:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems like the people of Seiran\Ndon't trust the New Himuka government at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.67,0:06:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But Major General Karen's reputation\Ngot him a lot of followers.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.67,0:06:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Where is Kasane?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.83,0:06:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No one has seen her after the gathering.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.50,0:06:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,My sister is somewhere in this city.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.79,0:07:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,CONNECTION FAILED
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.79,0:07:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The hero who assassinated\NChairman Sumeragi is on our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.25,0:07:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The higher-ups of Seiran are glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.08,0:07:21.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.83,0:07:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Does it matter if you get to be the hero?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.79,0:07:27.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Make use of that title.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.33,0:07:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Seiran is using me for their bidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.50,0:07:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't matter. Where is Naomi now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.63,0:07:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It has been confirmed that\Nabove the Kunad Highway
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.46,0:07:42.63,Default,,0,0,0,,is a partial singularity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.58,0:07:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's expanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.33,0:07:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.38,0:07:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's consuming everything around it and growing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.63,0:07:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,The New Himuka Government called it\Nthe Kunad Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.00,0:08:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing slowly grew without us\Neven noticing it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.04,0:08:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I created this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.67,0:08:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like a black hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.79,0:08:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called the Kunad Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.29,0:08:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see, the hold\Nis still consuming our world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.38,0:08:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.96,0:08:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Kasane, you've been to the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.63,0:08:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.83,0:08:23.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's not waste my time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.58,0:08:25.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.33,0:08:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,what did you see in the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.42,0:08:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,He can tell I've been to the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.08,0:08:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's futile to keep it a secret now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.29,0:08:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,At the end of the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.08,0:08:38.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I ran into you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.79,0:08:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What did my future self tell you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.42,0:08:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,There's hope after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.42,0:08:46.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you mean there was a chance\Nto save those who were turned into Others?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.79,0:08:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Karen, what more do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have a way to turn Others\Nback to human beings,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.92,0:08:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,then Naomi can be saved.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.17,0:09:00.92,Default,,0,0,0,,All I can tell you for now
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.92,0:09:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,is that researchers in Seiran
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.46,0:09:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,are conducting researches related to Others.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.04,0:09:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,That's where they keep Naomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, she is safe there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.04,0:09:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are they conducting the research?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.13,0:09:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.50,0:09:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The research is highly confidential.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.63,0:09:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Outsiders are not allowed into the facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.75,0:09:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I am no outsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.79,0:09:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell me, or I'll resort to violence.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.25,0:09:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,So here you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.54,0:09:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Arashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.29,0:09:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry to interrupt the conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.63,0:09:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time for our mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.21,0:09:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,We can set out for our mission\Nwithout the captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.38,0:09:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Arashi, keep an eye on this reckless brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.75,0:09:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Arashi, why did you stop me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.83,0:09:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You are always so reckless\Nwhen Naomi is involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.42,0:09:52.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I overheard everything.\NYou want to get into the facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.46,0:09:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You have all the more reason\Nnot to get into trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.21,0:09:56.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.29,0:10:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Before you start opposing your superior,\Nyou must act like an obedient soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.13,0:10:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you willing to help me get to Naomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.67,0:10:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Certainly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, she is one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.21,0:10:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll gather information about the facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.54,0:10:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,For the time being,\Nbehave and carry out your mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.67,0:10:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,"YUITO"\NThat's about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.67,0:10:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, there is no need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.33,0:10:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We will prescribe some medicine for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.96,0:10:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Take the pills when the symptoms show up.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.96,0:10:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.71,0:10:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.75,0:10:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, how was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It was caused by extreme fatigue.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.58,0:10:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Over-secretion of psionic hormone
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,caused the part of the brain\Nthat controls memories
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.38,0:10:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,become confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.42,0:10:59.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Some medication will get me back on my feet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.71,0:11:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.83,0:11:03.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.21,0:11:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.04,0:11:09.33,Default,,0,0,0,,MUSCLE DANCE
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.00,0:11:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thankfully it wasn't any serious condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.33,0:11:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand what the girls like nowadays.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.13,0:11:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Too much had happened since\Nyou joined the force.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.75,0:11:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It's normal if you feel exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.79,0:11:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You're low on spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,You need more water.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.75,0:11:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is everyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.21,0:11:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.79,0:11:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We carried out our mission\Nand completed the patrol.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.63,0:11:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsugumi was worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.29,0:11:58.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Does Yuito need a lot of water too?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.83,0:12:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You just got promoted,\Ndon't give yourself too much stress.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.25,0:12:04.58,Default,,0,0,0,,If there is anything we can help you with,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.58,0:12:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,feel free to tell us.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.46,0:12:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.63,0:12:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,During the turmoils in Suoh,\Nhe bravely fought against the Others.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.50,0:12:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,"A HERO IS BORN"\NHe's the hero of Suoh,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.21,0:12:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Private Yuito Sumeragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.46,0:12:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"2ND LIEUTENANT YUITO SUMERAGI, 16"\NBecause of his gallant feat, he's been promoted
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,"THE NATIONAL HERO APPOINTED AS CAPTAIN"\Nand appointed the captain of Platoon 01.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.83,0:12:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What? When did they interview me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.83,0:12:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no recollection of this at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.50,0:12:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Up next, we have footage of our national hero's\Nheroic combat on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.50,0:12:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, I know it leaves a bad taste in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.08,0:12:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But please bear with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.58,0:12:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You must become our national hero.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.96,0:12:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We lost the council and the Chairman.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.00,0:12:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Our people are in a panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.25,0:12:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You must become their beacon of hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.58,0:12:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But I still remember the conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.08,0:13:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Was there anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.04,0:13:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I can't recall any memory.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.92,0:13:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The traitor Kasane Randall\Nbrutally assassinated Chairman Sumeragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.88,0:13:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,2nd Lieutenant Yuito Sumeragi\Novercame the sadness of this tragedy
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.38,0:13:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,and stood out to fight for New Himuka's future.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.29,0:13:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't get to come here every day.\NWhy not take a tour around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.50,0:13:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me show you around.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.75,0:13:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a nice idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.67,0:13:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Rather than watching hyped-up news\Nby the Crows,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.75,0:13:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,a tour doesn't sound that bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.13,0:13:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.25,0:13:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes some time to get the medicine ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.83,0:13:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.29,0:13:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.00,0:13:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, how may I help you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.29,0:13:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,How do I get to the Neurology Department?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.83,0:14:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.96,0:14:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow the signs over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.21,0:14:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,NEUROLOGY
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.71,0:14:08.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I can't see it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.67,0:14:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because I'm a Bell Pepper...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.33,0:14:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't see signs that use\Nthe psionic system to operate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.75,0:14:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I can take you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.75,0:14:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, it won't take long.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.29,0:14:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,-Follow me.\N-I'm sorry for the trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The Vision Town and psynet,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.25,0:14:28.50,Default,,0,0,0,,and even Arahabaki
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.50,0:14:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,were created based on the presumption\Nthat everyone has access to brain powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.46,0:14:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,From what I heard, around 0.1% of the population\Nare Bell Peppers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.04,0:14:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The government should care more\Nabout the minority.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.50,0:14:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,"NEUROLOGY"\NHere we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.13,0:14:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.75,0:14:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.00,0:14:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.38,0:14:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,AUTHORIZED PERSONNEL ONLY
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.42,0:15:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.38,0:15:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You saw Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.42,0:15:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They took him to an elevator\Nthat leads to the underground.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.96,0:15:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Could I have mistaken someone for him?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.92,0:15:27.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I can't get any access.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.96,0:15:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't get into the hospital's system.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.25,0:15:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I found it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi is in the underground tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.46,0:15:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He's been brought onto a car.\NI don't know where they are headed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.33,0:16:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Underground tunnels lead to the city area.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.46,0:16:02.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know which direction they went?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.83,0:16:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.75,0:16:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they are headed to Lokusho City.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.04,0:16:12.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Lokusho City?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.13,0:16:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The city that was destroyed instantly\Nafter the Other attacked 11 years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.04,0:16:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito, you and your mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.13,0:16:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,There is an old facility of the OSF hospital\Nin Lokusho City.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.71,0:16:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.63,0:16:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I remember correctly,\Nthat place has been abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.75,0:16:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I think so too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.21,0:16:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If Nagi is really there,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.13,0:16:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,if he's still alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.63,0:16:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I must talk to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.58,0:16:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope everyone could come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.79,0:16:51.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the abandoned OSF hospital facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.92,0:16:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nothing around it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.29,0:16:58.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought the Others are only\Ninterested in human brains.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.63,0:17:01.21,Default,,0,0,0,,How did it become so desolate?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.79,0:17:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I found the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.38,0:17:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,But Nagi is not in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.75,0:17:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he inside the building?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.96,0:17:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,There are places I can't see through.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.54,0:17:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So this place is still operating.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.50,0:17:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.96,0:17:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard rumors.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.96,0:17:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Some kind of institute seemed to conduct\Nexperiments in this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.88,0:17:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The surrounding buildings might\Nhave been removed
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.21,0:17:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,by the New Himuka Government.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.29,0:17:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wataru, can you check\Nwhat's inside the building?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.46,0:17:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't access the data about this old facility.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.04,0:17:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I advise you to be cautious.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.75,0:17:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.96,0:17:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.50,0:17:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll proceed with cautions.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.92,0:18:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,This is incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.71,0:18:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's consuming everything around it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.46,0:18:17.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What happens to the things that go in there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.79,0:18:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right, Shiden.\NTry putting your hand in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.50,0:18:24.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you stick your head into it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.08,0:18:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.21,0:18:28.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop fooling around, and don't get too close.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.63,0:18:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Curiosity kills the cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.50,0:18:33.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I remember this feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.67,0:18:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I felt it when the Red Strings were triggered.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.71,0:18:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That means...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.50,0:18:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Our powers
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.67,0:18:48.21,Default,,0,0,0,,share the same property of manipulating gravity.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.21,0:18:50.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Our powers resonated
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.38,0:18:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,and gave birth to the Kunad Gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.04,0:18:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The future Yuito was right after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.04,0:18:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's on your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.17,0:19:04.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you thinking about the Kunad Gate\Nyou saw in the future?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.13,0:19:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's when you met the future Yuito.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.17,0:19:09.88,Default,,0,0,0,,He was like a different person.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.88,0:19:12.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't care if he lost his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.33,0:19:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel sad for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.92,0:19:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you plan to take his life\Nbefore he turns into that sorry state?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.13,0:19:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So he won't feel any pain?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.33,0:19:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.21,0:19:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You must live on.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.33,0:19:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That person and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.21,0:19:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.92,0:19:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,We have intruders. What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.71,0:20:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong, Yuito?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.63,0:20:12.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this place remind you\Nof the time you spent in the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.38,0:20:15.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's impossible. I was too young back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.17,0:20:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't remember what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.00,0:20:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Above us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.79,0:20:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuito!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.38,0:20:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, I can only see through\Nthe horizontal areas.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.04,0:20:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Hanabi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.08,0:20:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't mention it. Stay alert.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.00,0:20:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.42,0:21:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The reaction became stronger.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.17,0:21:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The singularity is expanding.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.04,0:21:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How did this happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.42,0:21:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.04,0:21:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Kunad Gate, growth rate increased by 5%.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.33,0:22:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.33,0:22:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I don't need to let fate dictate me♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.00,0:22:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Because I believe that I can rewrite it♫
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.71,0:22:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,♫I'll always be a dreamer now and forever♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.21,0:23:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Another sunrise shines now and it blacks out♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.75,0:23:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♫What's waiting for us at the world's end♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.83,0:23:27.83,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Forever eternal, keep the fire going♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.83,0:23:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Who can shake us♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.21,0:23:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Who can define us♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.63,0:23:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,♫It's nothing less than our story♫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.58,0:23:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,♫Forever eternal,\Nkeep the fire going in your heart♫
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.08,0:24:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,TRUTH HIDDEN IN THE HOSPITAL
